data.description: Residential home located close to HWY 46 easy access to IH 10, Navarro ISD, and outside city limits. This property is perfect for those seeking a peaceful and comfortable lifestyle with plenty of space, this home counts with 4 bedrooms,3 bathrooms, office room with a build in desk and bookshelf, large living room for the family gatherings, dining room, second living area, plenty of space in kitchen with island, breakfast bar and all appliances included, separate laundry room. Mature trees, large fully fenced backyard, with a front porch. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this your home.
